snippet: The Wall Street bank was helped by the same active trading conditions that have helped its competitors.
abstract: Morgan Stanely reports revenue in first quarter jumped to highest since 2007, with $2.31 billion in profit, compared with $1.45 billion in period year earlier.

headline.main: Morgan Stanley Profit Jumps on Higher Trading Revenue
